HEADWORD: Fisher
<hw>Fish"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>fiscere</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who fishes.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A carnivorous animal of the
Weasel family (<spn>Mustela Canadensis</spn>); the pekan; the
⟦ldquo⟧black cat.⟦rdquo⟧</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Fisherman</ent>⟦br⟧
